<subSubSection id="D07AF43027A7B0DEDE3CF9E6BCBE43F5" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817" type="taxon discussion">
<paragraph id="9A38C9DC112C063B60B3E079E2A3C18F" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817">Taxon discussion</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3A713AC2F03977CF80BB6E71BEDBB1F4" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817">
Endemic to the Balkan Peninsula and Italy (
<bibRefCitation id="CBA753C8D076BBB8DF72CB803839E073" author="Bartolucci, F." journalOrPublisher="Plant Biosystems - An International Journal Dealing with all Aspects of Plant Biology" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817" pagination="179 - 303" refId="B7733034" refString="Bartolucci, F., Peruzzi, L., Galasso, G., Albano, A., Alessandrini, A., Ardenghi, N. M. G., Astuti, G., Bacchetta, G., Ballelli, S., Banfi, E., Barberis, G., Bernardo, L., Bouvet, D., Bovio, M., Cecchi, L., Pietro, R. Di, Domina, G., Fascetti, S., Fenu, G., Festi, F., Foggi, B., Gallo, L., Gottschlich, G., Gubellini, L., Iamonico, D., Iberite, M., Jimenez-Mejias, P., Lattanzi, E., Marchetti, D., Martinetto, E., Masin, R. R., Medagli, P., Passalacqua, N. G., Peccenini, S., Pennesi, R., Pierini, B., Poldini, L., Prosser, F., Raimondo, F. M., Roma-Marzio, F., Rosati, L., Santangelo, A., Scoppola, A., Scortegagna, S., Selvaggi, A., Selvi, F., Soldano, A., Stinca, A., Wagensommer, R. P., Wilhalm, T., Conti, F., 2018. An updated checklist of the vascular flora native to Italy. Plant Biosystems - An International Journal Dealing with all Aspects of Plant Biology 152 (2): 179 - 303" title="An updated checklist of the vascular flora native to Italy" volume="152" year="2018">Bartolucci et al. 2018</bibRefCitation>
), 
<taxonomicName id="7B9A6527A1BCF0F6956B087FB7FA5B25" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Orobanchaceae" genus="Pedicularis" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Pedicularis friderici-augusti" order="Lamiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="friderici-augusti">
<emphasis id="CA5B3422360D501248263A834631F7F2" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817">Pedicularis friderici-augusti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is rare in Greece, as it has been recorded so far from only three mountains of the NE floristic region: Menikio, Falakro and Orvilos (
<bibRefCitation id="28D4110BB70E45EE65E6976EA1604C4B" author="Raus, T." journalOrPublisher="Edinburgh University Press, Edinburgh" pageId="0" pageNumber="81817" refId="B7669266" refString="Raus, T., 1991. Mountain Flora of Greece 2. Edinburgh University Press, Edinburgh" title="Mountain Flora of Greece 2" year="1991">Raus 1991</bibRefCitation>
). This is the fourth record in the Greek territory, on a different mountain and the easternmost border of the 
<normalizedToken id="AE5E533C3BC7518A2B1C08AD5D0A54F6" originalValue="species’">species'</normalizedToken>
distribution in the country.
</paragraph>
